    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle St&#8212;Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1887-05-03"><name type="place">U S America</name> May 3 '87<ptr
                            target="uva.00557_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Yours of Ap: 20 just rec'd &#38; welcomed.<ptr target="uva.00557_n2"/> Write
                oftener&#8212;The Staffords<ptr target="uva.00557_n3"/> &#38; I remember you with
                greatest affection &#38; esteem&#8212;I also with deepest gratitude&#8212;I am still
                here in the same little old house&#8212;of course gradually sinking &#38;
                dissolving&#8212;Harry S[tafford]<ptr target="n0590"/> had a surgical operation on
                his throat&#8212;it seems to have been properly done, &#38; the cut is
                healing&#8212;He is at Marlton, New Jersey, married, has a child&#8212;I send you
                some papers&#8212;always best love&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
